     .

         National Information Technology Forum
         Building Smarter in the Digital Age
         E-Governance Focuses on Building Regulatory System in
         National Forum on Building Smarter in the Digital Age.
         May 31 - June 1, 2001, Hilton Crystal City at National Airport
         Arlington (Crystal City), Virginia
     .

         Building Stone of the United States: The NIST Test Wall.  The wall
         provides a rare opportunity to study the effects of weathering on
         different types of stones, with the climatic conditions being the same
         for all stones.
     .

         The Building Integrated Photovoltaic Weather Station provides
         meteorological data models used to predict the electrical performance
         of building integrated photovoltaic panels.
     .

